OK, 
I have a good 12 Volt 1600 Dp engine which I want to put into a 6 volt 66 Kombi. 
Can I really just take the 6 volt flywheel and put it on the 12 volt 
engine?  What else would need to be changed out?  Voltage 
Regulator, Bulbs, Wiper motor?

